trans-unit.target: Expone los tipos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> a la automatización de la interfaz de usuario.

trans-unit.source: The element associated with this automation peer.
trans-unit.target: El elemento asociado a este nivel de automatización.

trans-unit.source: The automation peer that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControlGroup" /> that holds the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" />.
trans-unit.target: Automatización del mismo nivel asociada al <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControlGroup" /> que contiene el <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control type for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el tipo de control correspondiente al control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the class name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el nombre de clase del objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> asociado con <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: The class name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Nombre de clase del objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: A value enumeration that specifies the control pattern.
trans-unit.target: Enumeración de valor que especifica el patrón de control.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el patrón de control de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> que está asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: An object that supports the control pattern if <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is the <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" /> value; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto que admite el patrón de control si <paramref name="patternInterface" /> es el valor <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" />; en caso contrario, <see langword="null" />.
